{"tid":94855,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]江西化工廠硫酸洩漏　51人不適1人死亡","createTime":"2017-01-25T13:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T06:32:55.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"593302dc72feb8a986b05ebe503ee3909097a6bd","tid":94855,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:56:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170125/bkncn-20170125192852350-0125_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170125%2Fbkncn-20170125192852350-0125_05011_001.html&d=oudMuPEce2JXF3%2FcKJezMn8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=1a0a26d0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170125/bkncn-20170125192852350-0125_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170125/photo/bkncn-20170125192852350-0125_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170125%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170125192852350-0125_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=37aa6971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n江西三美化工有限公司（小圖）發生高濃度硫酸洩漏。圖為該廠早前進行應急演習。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n江西贛州市興國縣一間化工廠，昨晚發生高濃度硫酸洩漏，截至今日中午12時，已有51人感到不適被送院。其中40人留院醫治（當中8人情況嚴重），其中1人經搶救無效死亡，另11人接受門診觀察。目前，事故原因仍在調查。<br />\n<br />\n據興國縣政府通報，昨晚10時左右，江西三美化工有限公司一輛運載高濃度硫酸的大型貨車，在將硫酸卸入儲存罐時，突然發生放熱反應，造成部分水蒸氣和煙氣外洩。<br />\n<br />\n涉事公司得悉後，立即組織工廠員工進行處理洩漏的硫酸，在1個小時後控制了放熱反應。惟多名處理洩漏的員工事後出現身體不適，需送院治理。興國縣委、縣政府主要官員亦隨即趕到現場指揮救援及善後工作，並調查事故原因。<br />\n<br />\n過唔到年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11db2fcc3a03c8d8a94a2007884d50dbb243b828","tid":94855,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"真相可能係 51死1傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753a59196f49bedbc635348e1cb1e635ac1dfa4d","tid":94855,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67060381f24200e8f841c7fd7a46116a43bc7c54","tid":94855,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a1619be34e06913dd974f44ffe50efe3c80894","tid":94855,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5686ba186a921e4d2ab2afb362f768d5213de7d","tid":94855,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:34:24.000Z","msg":"即係稀釋硫酸，點解會死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61381ea5376f51afa2d6fc0a83a871675afffe7","tid":94855,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:32:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}